reviews.review_text: Happy Times Done Justice Always a favorite AUD of mine, to find this outstanding mix with an equally crispy SBD just fills me with joy.  Thank you so much for this one.  Excellent work.  Sound is just about as good as they get.  The show?  One of the best from this run, IMHO.  The famous Loser that was left off the commercial release stands as one of the best of any era (again, IMHO).  The whole show just jumps right out of the gate and doesn't let up til the very end.  Happy, happy, happy.
better than commercial the title says it all!!! great show-thanks a million good job!5 stars for 1990

Why Is This Gone? I will not pull down the rating of this outstanding show (thus the 5 stars) but it is truly absurd that even a Matrix gets pulled because a portion of this show was commercially released.  ARGH!!
Thanks. Greedy Dead Merchandising and Rhino strike again!  What a sick f$*&ing joke our corporate culture has become.
